<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.37.7935.figs1-9>
    dc:description "Figs 1 - 9. Catatinagma stenoptera sp. n. 1. Adult, holotype. 2. Head, lateral view. 3. Head, view from above; 4. Male sternum VIII (gen. slide 55 / 11). 5. Female tergum VII (gen. slide 56 / 11). 6. Male sternum I + II (gen. slide 55 / 11). 7. Male tergum I (gen. slide 55 / 11). 8. Male genitalia (gen. slide 55 / 11). 9. Female genitalia (gen. slide 56 / 11)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/8192" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

